@page
@model IndexModel
@{
    ViewData["Title"] = "Home Page";
}

    <div class="alert alert-primary alert-dismissible fade show" style="background-color:rgba(0, 255, 255,0.2)" role="alert">
        <p class="mb-0 text-dark">Advice : @Model.advice</p>
        <button type="button" class="close" data-dismiss="alert" aria-label="Close">
            <span aria-hidden="true">&times;</span>
        </button>
    </div>

    <div class="card-columns">  
        <div class="card">
            <div class="card-body">
                <h5 class="card-title">Our goal!</h5>
                <p class="card-text">Our goals (why we made this site) </p>
                <img class="card-img-top" src="/img/shaggy.jpg">
                <p class="card-text">Cause no one challenge us!<br />....<br /> JK we just have nothing else to do primarly in our nerd life</p>
            </div>
        </div>
        <div class="card">
            <img class="card-img-top" src="/img/main page.jpg" >
            <div class="card-body">
                <h5 class="card-title">What do we do ?</h5>
                <p class="card-text">
                    Diagnostic errors are the 6th leading cause of death in the United States and contribute to 80,000 deaths annually.
                    We wanted to reduce that (don't worry we planned to do it for the entire world not only the US like in the movies)
                    This website helps keep track of each individual what sickness he/she/it has/had (yes we are going to support pets and animals soon^^) where was the last
                    they visited a doctor or had a medical check We wanted to to have all the important information that the doctors will need inorder to treat you.
                </p>
            </div>
        </div>
        <div class="card bg-primary text-white text-center p-3">
            <blockquote class="blockquote mb-0">
                <p>The purpose of life is not to be happy. It is to be useful, to be honorable, to be compassionate, to have it make some difference that you have lived and lived well.</p>
                <footer class="blockquote-footer">
                    <small>
                        Ralph Waldo Emerson
                    </small>
                </footer>
            </blockquote>
        </div>
        <div class="card">
            <div class="card-body">
                <h5 class="card-title">Made by</h5>
                <p class="card-text">This website was a great idea and yet again ignored, Why you may ask well that's how the world rules <small class="text-muted">as George Carlin</small> “The caterpillar does all the work, but the butterfly gets all the publicity.”</p>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>

